<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 04:08:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡为了空洞的口号和政治利益牺牲了加沙的以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-sacrificed-the-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-for-empty-slogans-and-political-gain/0000018d-8047-d636-adef-ceef8b310000</link><description>《纽约时报》有关仍被哈马斯俘虏的以色列人命运的报道对于政界或军事界的任何人来说都不足为奇。家人声称“时间不多了”的说法在今天听起来截然不同</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 04:02:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-sacrificed-the-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-for-empty-slogans-and-political-gain/0000018d-8047-d636-adef-ceef8b310000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡拒绝调解努力，人质家属加大力度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-to-intensify-their-campaign-as-netanyahu-rebuffs-mediation-efforts/0000018d-8003-daa1-a9fd-e20baf6b0000</link><description>哈马斯再次要求结束加沙战争作为释放人质的先决条件，而总理部分出于政治原因表示反对。即使是过渡时期似乎也遥遥无期 ■ 有报道称，在囚禁期间死亡的人质人数比以色列承认的还要多，政府似乎对战争失去了兴趣</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 04:01:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-to-intensify-their-campaign-as-netanyahu-rebuffs-mediation-efforts/0000018d-8003-daa1-a9fd-e20baf6b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列正在审查哈马斯对停火、人质提议的反应；以色列国防军军官在加沙战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article-live/israel-reviewing-hamas-response-to-hostage-proposal-idf-officer-killed-in-gaza/0000018d-8196-d6dc-ab9f-cfff8a840000</link><description>沙特阿拉伯表示，如果没有巴勒斯坦建国，就不会与以色列建立任何关系 ■ 拜登称哈马斯对协议的反应“有点过分” ■ 战时内阁成员甘茨：目标是在以色列没有民事权力的情况下对加沙进行全面安全控制 ■ 纽约时报报道：以色列正在评估是否加沙至少20名人质被杀，另有32人确认死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 03:34:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article-live/israel-reviewing-hamas-response-to-hostage-proposal-idf-officer-killed-in-gaza/0000018d-8196-d6dc-ab9f-cfff8a840000</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院未能通过共和党向以色列提供 170 亿美元独立援助的努力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-house-fails-to-pass-gop-effort-to-provide-israel-with-17b-in-standalone-aid/0000018d-80c6-d6dc-ab9f-cfffec3b0000</link><description>鉴于参议院民主党人坚持将以色列援助纳入拜登总统的国家安全补充援助计划（其中包括超过 140 亿美元的以色列援助），该法案获得推进的机会为零</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 23:58:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-house-fails-to-pass-gop-effort-to-provide-israel-with-17b-in-standalone-aid/0000018d-80c6-d6dc-ab9f-cfffec3b0000</guid></item><item><title>由于担心冒犯宗教预备役军人，以色列国防军取消了女性表演</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/idf-cancels-womens-performance-for-fear-of-offending-religious-reservists/0000018d-8059-daa1-a9fd-e25b6ce40000</link><description>驻扎在北部的该营的士兵们请求举办一场退役派对，其中包括爱情旅的表演，但最终却得到了右翼演讲者和一名恐同拉比的一系列讲座。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 23:23:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/idf-cancels-womens-performance-for-fear-of-offending-religious-reservists/0000018d-8059-daa1-a9fd-e25b6ce40000</guid></item><item><title>美国对极端主义定居者的制裁使以色列极右翼财政部长陷入困境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-sanctions-on-extremist-settlers-put-israels-far-right-finance-minister-in-a-bind/0000018d-801b-d6dc-ab9f-cf7f01d60000</link><description>以色列国民银行冻结了四名涉嫌暴力定居者之一的账户后，财政部长贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇发誓要采取行动，但他所能做的就是试图说服美国当局，因为他在美国不受欢迎</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 23:07:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-sanctions-on-extremist-settlers-put-israels-far-right-finance-minister-in-a-bind/0000018d-801b-d6dc-ab9f-cf7f01d60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列寻求切断加沙对近东救济工程处的依赖，但尚不清楚谁可以取代它</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-seeks-to-sever-gazas-dependency-on-unrwa-but-its-unclear-who-could-replace-it/0000018d-8059-d636-adef-ceff82270000</link><description>这一想法是试图切断哈马斯与进入加沙地带的人道主义援助的一部分，战时内阁成员在这一问题上达成了共识。一位消息人士告诉《国土报》，世界粮食计划署在加沙缺乏必要的基础设施来取代该机构的活动</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 22:21:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-seeks-to-sever-gazas-dependency-on-unrwa-but-its-unclear-who-could-replace-it/0000018d-8059-d636-adef-ceff82270000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列问题上，拜登继续选择胡萝卜而不是大棒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-06/ty-article/.highlight/biden-keeps-on-choosing-the-carrot-over-stick-when-it-comes-to-israel/0000018d-7f91-d636-adef-7fffb8290000</link><description>对于那些希望拜登最终利用军事援助作为筹码的人来说，参议院的一揽子计划还有很多不足之处</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 21:09:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-06/ty-article/.highlight/biden-keeps-on-choosing-the-carrot-over-stick-when-it-comes-to-israel/0000018d-7f91-d636-adef-7fffb8290000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军命名在加沙地带北部战斗中丧生的以色列军官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-israeli-officer-killed-in-northern-gaza-strip-fighting/0000018d-8016-d6dc-ab9f-cf7f95a20000</link><description>大卫·沙库里少校是陆军第401装甲旅作战工程兵第601营副营长。他的朋友这样评价他：“一位举止冷静的指挥官，树立了榜样”</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 21:03:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-israeli-officer-killed-in-northern-gaza-strip-fighting/0000018d-8016-d6dc-ab9f-cf7f95a20000</guid></item><item><title>海法市迫于压力阻止有关以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突的新书发行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/haifa-municipality-thwarts-book-launch-on-israeli-palestinian-conflict-amid-pressure/0000018d-7fa2-daa1-a9fd-7faa3d1c0000</link><description>在市内政党的压力下，市政府宣布“推迟活动”，但没有确定新的日期。民权协会猛烈抨击此举，而右翼分子则赞扬此举</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 20:40:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/haifa-municipality-thwarts-book-launch-on-israeli-palestinian-conflict-amid-pressure/0000018d-7fa2-daa1-a9fd-7faa3d1c0000</guid></item><item><title>在人质交易方面，保持权力始终是内塔尼亚胡最关心的问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/when-it-comes-to-hostage-deals-staying-in-power-is-always-netanyahus-paramount-concern/0000018d-7fbe-d636-adef-7ffeaf910000</link><description>从 1985 年开始，本杰明·内塔尼亚胡在其政治生涯中参与了三起人质交易。他对与哈马斯潜在的新人质交易的立场仍然是个谜，但他肯定会研究民意调查，为自己找出最佳选择</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 19:50:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/when-it-comes-to-hostage-deals-staying-in-power-is-always-netanyahus-paramount-concern/0000018d-7fbe-d636-adef-7ffeaf910000</guid></item><item><title>以色列审查哈马斯对加沙停火、人质协议的反应；拜登：“似乎有点过头了”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/israel-reviews-hamas-response-to-hostage-deal-biden-seems-a-little-over-the-top/0000018d-7f91-d6dc-ab9f-7ffd246e0000</link><description>在与最近一次访问中东的美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯会面后，卡塔尔总理补充说，哈马斯的反应“总体上是积极的”。他没有提供更多细节，但指出哈马斯对拟议交易有“评论”</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 19:47:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/israel-reviews-hamas-response-to-hostage-deal-biden-seems-a-little-over-the-top/0000018d-7f91-d6dc-ab9f-7ffd246e0000</guid></item><item><title>第一批定居者，现在是网络：美国威胁取消间谍软件制造商的入境签证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/first-settlers-now-cyber-u-s-threatens-to-cancel-entry-visas-for-spyware-makers/0000018d-7f25-daa1-a9fd-7f2fd9640000</link><description>尽管美国长期以来一直寻求遏制间谍软件公司，并将 NSO 和 Intellexa 等公司列入黑名单，但以色列进攻性网络行业的消息人士表示，新政策是拜登和内塔尼亚胡之间紧张关系的一部分</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 19:30:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/first-settlers-now-cyber-u-s-threatens-to-cancel-entry-visas-for-spyware-makers/0000018d-7f25-daa1-a9fd-7f2fd9640000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯访问以色列：预计将讨论人质谈判、加沙计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/blinken-visits-israel-expected-to-discuss-hostages-gaza-war-and-day-after-plans/0000018d-7ee0-d636-adef-7eeecd300000</link><description>这是美国国务卿自10月7日以来第五次访问中东，美国和以色列正在考虑哈马斯对人质和停火协议的反应</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 18:08:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/blinken-visits-israel-expected-to-discuss-hostages-gaza-war-and-day-after-plans/0000018d-7ee0-d636-adef-7eeecd300000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 123 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-123/0000018d-7f91-daa1-a9fd-7f9b7eba0000</link><description>据以色列国防军、《纽约时报》报道，加沙剩余人质中至少有 32 名人质死亡 ■ 哈马斯对人质释放/停火协议作出“积极”回应 ■ 据报道，以色列向美国和联合国施压，要求允许近东救济工程处继续向加沙提供援助 ■ 绝大多数的以色列人认为下一次选举应该更早举行 ■ 战争结束 123 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 17:57:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-123/0000018d-7f91-daa1-a9fd-7f9b7eba0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 123 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-123/0000018d-7f86-d636-adef-7fee8ff00000</link><description>据《纽约时报》报道，根据以色列国防军的评估，加沙剩余人质中至少有 32 名人质死亡 ■ 哈马斯表示，它对拟议的人质释放/停火协议做出了“积极”回应 ■ 据报道，以色列正在向以色列施压美国和联合国允许近东救济工程处继续向加沙提供人道主义援助 ■ 绝大多数以色列人认为，下一次选举应该比指定日期 2026 年 11 月早得多举行 ■ 战争结束 123 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 17:54:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-123/0000018d-7f86-d636-adef-7fee8ff00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡抨击以色列国防军模拟以色列定居者绑架巴勒斯坦人的演习，要求调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-slams-idf-for-drill-simulating-settler-kidnapping-palestinian-demands-probe/0000018d-7f32-daa1-a9fd-7f3ad9e40000</link><description>以色列国防军发言人表示，此次演习是旨在提高西岸师战备状态的大规模演习的一部分。他补充说，“演练了 100 多种不同的场景，包括极端场景”</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 17:40:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-slams-idf-for-drill-simulating-settler-kidnapping-palestinian-demands-probe/0000018d-7f32-daa1-a9fd-7f3ad9e40000</guid></item><item><title>“如果以色列不提供替代方案，加沙陷入混乱，我们最终将再次陷入哈马斯统治”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-02-06/ty-article-podcast/if-we-dont-offer-an-alternative-to-chaos-in-gaza-well-end-up-with-hamas-rule-again/0000018d-7eaa-d6dc-ab9f-7fff5ee50000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 17:13:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-02-06/ty-article-podcast/if-we-dont-offer-an-alternative-to-chaos-in-gaza-well-end-up-with-hamas-rule-again/0000018d-7eaa-d6dc-ab9f-7fff5ee50000</guid></item><item><title>由于以色列封锁资金，巴勒斯坦权力机构将减少公共部门工人的工资</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/palestinian-authority-to-pay-reduced-salaries-as-israel-blocks-funds/0000018d-7f19-d6dc-ab9f-7f7d28fa0000</link><description>以色列财政部长指责拉马拉支持哈马斯，并拒绝释放以色列代表巴勒斯坦人征收的税收资金。巴勒斯坦权力机构表示，“将继续致力于保护囚犯和烈士以及加沙地带的人民”</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 17:05:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/palestinian-authority-to-pay-reduced-salaries-as-israel-blocks-funds/0000018d-7f19-d6dc-ab9f-7f7d28fa0000</guid></item><item><title>这些年轻的特拉维夫艺术家正在面对 10 月 7 日和加沙战争的恐怖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/these-young-tel-aviv-artists-are-confronting-the-horrors-of-oct-7-and-the-gaza-war/0000018d-7e4b-d636-adef-7eef6f7d0000</link><description>五位来自不同领域的新兴艺术家饱受创伤和悲伤的折磨，正在努力应对哈马斯的袭击和随后的加沙战争。但正如其中一位所宣称的那样，“战后以色列艺术的一个历史时期将从这里出现”</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 16:44:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/these-young-tel-aviv-artists-are-confronting-the-horrors-of-oct-7-and-the-gaza-war/0000018d-7e4b-d636-adef-7eef6f7d0000</guid></item></channel></rss>